		"description": "<p>You touch a creature and stimulate its natural Healing ability. The target regains 4d8 + 15 Hit Points. For the Duration of the spell, the target regains 1 hit point at the start of each of its turns (10 hit points each minute).</p><p>The target's severed body members (fingers, legs, tails, and so on), if any, are restored after 2 minutes. If you have the severed part and hold it to the stump, the spell instantaneously causes the limb to knit to the stump.</p>",
